  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your stubbornness to never back down yields to no one. Once per short rest, you can cast any jutsu that requires an attack roll or imposes a saving throw, and casting of 1 action, as a reaction, granting it the clash keyword. If the jutsu already has the clash keyword, add a 1d4 to your clash check. Starting at 11th level, once per turn, while you are at 50% or less of your current hit points, you can roll a Constitution (Survival) check against a DC of 25. (This check cannot benefit from expertise.) On a success, you activate your <em><strong>Zenkai Boost</strong></em>. <br />Starting at 18th level, when you initiate a clash, you roll at advantage.</p>",
